{"tid":513750,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"分享大家嘅靈異事件 有主持人占卜時段。。「限定九點」1872遊花園「私服」","createTime":"2017-12-30T00:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-06T18:05:14.000Z","uid":107494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"82173622b510f7363552952b23f5840388dfe957","tid":513750,"uid":107494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T00:59:44.000Z","msg":"一向我地開台時間都係凌晨一點 <br />\n但係因為上個星期請假一天 <br />\n所以今日節目時間將會改做<span style=\"color: red;\">下午九時</span>正開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 熱烈地彈琴熱烈地唱<br />\n<br />\n上次開台阿瑋就講古怪事 氣氛不錯 大家都幾鐘意聽鬼故 同有唔同既聽眾分享<br />\n<br />\n如果想重溫 次次都加時<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MtE8xB-1qzc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMtE8xB-1qzc&d=aM7vva%2FQTNmAI2Cu%2Fh29SW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=680dea4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MtE8xB-1qzc</a><br />\n<br />\n各位聽眾只要加毒蘋果的skype<br />\n「llae86ll@gmail.com」<br />\n或者Telegram <br />\n@LonelyApple<br />\n就可以係節目期間致電就可以一齊討論咁有趣嘅題目 所有聽眾都會經過監製篩選<br />\nps:讚佢靚女接聽機會大大提高(可能<br />\n<br />\n主持人包括: <br />\n白雪 公仔 阿瑋<br />\n<br />\n每次討論既主題類型都唔同 仲會有好多唔同既活動環節 如果各位有興趣 不妨聯絡我大家一齊商討或者加入FB <br />\n<br />\nFB &ldquo;獨蘋果 LApple&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"http://facebook.com/%E7%8D%A8%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9CLApple-1904427313216701\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2F%25E7%258D%25A8%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259CLApple-1904427313216701&d=aM7vva%2FQTNmAI2Cu%2Fh29SW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=26e4c2d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">facebook.com/%E7%8D%A8%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9CLApple-1904427313216701</a><br />\n<br />\n希望各位捧下場 過黎食住花生 談笑風生<br />\n<a href=\"http://youtube.com/channel/UCksXp1cIh0Zx06Ups7KydIA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCksXp1cIh0Zx06Ups7KydIA&d=aM7vva%2FQTNmAI2Cu%2Fh29SW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=8e7907b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">youtube.com/channel/UCksXp1cIh0Zx06Ups7KydIA</a>"},{"pid":"00dc6077d55dc8295c12a124ca1098dcfcfccc48","tid":513750,"uid":107494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T01:00:14.000Z","msg":"1872 遊花園（私服）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/469419/page/10?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/469419/page/10?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bff63a73e9de5660705852f149397d9abca2a7cc","tid":513750,"uid":107494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T01:01:36.000Z","msg":"今晚性誕後 大家可以講下做咗啲咩傻事喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cec1d95ef4c2c6d055a4d46b0ec36530a99a7ab","tid":513750,"uid":107494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T01:03:24.000Z","msg":"之前話希望提早開台既巴打今晚記得捧場<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc69f0182d0b58be65742db0f9c3929d7430c5de","tid":513750,"uid":107494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T04:10:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d4e050d0c082af2749b2bb31ee9635f05d61af1","tid":513750,"uid":107494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T07:58:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"71e09893d10713cf3d889d8fe3037570d9ada666","tid":513750,"uid":107494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T11:07:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0693a5d688c893e90764355c2d385b5fd3e659b3","tid":513750,"uid":107494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T12:15:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02e1a82874257b4405e3c8b5752804c5a90856c2","tid":513750,"uid":107494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T12:15:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aaf085fffc188a3a5acc44bf47753e7f081d6988","tid":513750,"uid":107494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T12:59:28.000Z","msg"